&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Coordinate and execute employee wellness initiatives and recognition programs throughout the year&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Manage the employee engagement calendar and logistics for company-sponsored events and wellness activiti

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Vision&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;P\S\L Group is a global organisation dedicated to putting information at the service of medicine. The companies and people of the P\S\L Group aim to improve medical care by serving those who need it, those who provide it and those who seek to improve it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our primary purpose is to help clients increase the effectiveness of activities pertaining to scientific communication, medical education and product/service marketing. To this end, we want our information services to contribute to the goals we share with our clients, namely: to accelerate the advancement of medicine and help people enjoy better, longer lives.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;FirstWord belongs to the P\S\L Group and is a leading provider of news and market intelligence to the global pharmaceutical industry. Over 180,000 clients rely on FirstWord to stay well informed every business day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;FirstWord is a progressive, fast-growth company. It sets ambitious targets that it pursues vigorously. The entrepreneurial, opportunity-focused, customer-driven culture makes FirstWord a stimulating and enjoyable place in which high achievers develop and thrive. Career development potential, rewards and benefits reflect the quality of people who join the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Objective&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for high-energy, driven professionals with sound business acumen, strong technical aptitude and natural sales instincts. As a Sales Consultant you will act as part of a Regional Sales Team hunting new business within specific life science territories. Ideal candidates should be eager to advance in our organization by demonstrating their ability to be tenacious self-starters every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be the first point of contact between FirstWord Group and potential new clients at the beginning of our sales cycle. You will be the voice of the company focusing on uncovering unmet needs for our customers becoming a product and industry expert in the process, using that knowledge to win new business opportunities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will play a key role in further building the client base for FirstWord in your market with the responsibility of:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building new business leads from accounts that have not yet been penetrated.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cold-calling &amp;amp; emailing C-Level Executives and Key Decision Makers to open up new accounts and opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying and closing new prospects for meetings/demos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promptly follow-up on inbound leads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Closing new business opportunities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver scalable long-term growth, uncover and exploit new revenue streams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver on Forecasts to the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic Account Development: build an account plan and devise a strategy for transformational growth. Understand your Client(s) inside/out; its strategic initiatives, exec LT, culture, key brands / pipeline assets and processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify key business questions to develop new partnerships and draw on the appropriate internal resources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-functional stakeholder management: communicate and collaborate effectively with your team and the wider organization, build strong internal networks to influence strategic direction and partner with marketing, editorial and analyst teams to optimize the client journey.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
