&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;About Answers in CME&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Answers in CME (AiCME) is part of the P\S\L Group. AiCME is an independent company organized to develop and deliver independent education designed to positively impact patient outcomes. We follow rigorous standards and provide a fair and balanced view of therapeutic options, independent of any commercial interest.&lt;/p&gt;
